Creating our first POD.
aditygau@DESKTOP-5RVD1VH:/mnt/d/PROJECT/kubernetes_learning$ kubectl run nginx --image=nginx
pod/nginx created


aditygau@DESKTOP-5RVD1VH:/mnt/d/PROJECT/kubernetes_learning$ kubectl get pods          #this command is to monitor our pods
NAME    READY   STATUS    RESTARTS   AGE
nginx   1/1     Running   0          60s


aditygau@DESKTOP-5RVD1VH:/mnt/d/PROJECT/kubernetes_learning$ kubectl get pods -o wide            #to get extra details of the pods
NAME    READY   STATUS    RESTARTS   AGE    IP           NODE       NOMINATED NODE   READINESS GATES
nginx   1/1     Running   0          2m2s   10.244.0.3   minikube   <none>           <none>


We can we the command :  "kubectl describe pod" to get the complete details about the our pods

#clean-up

aditygau@DESKTOP-5RVD1VH:/mnt/d/PROJECT/kubernetes_learning$ kubectl delete pod nginx
pod "nginx" deleted from default namespace

